page.title: 11Birds in Voe.
page.content: Here are only a few of the birds which can be seen in Voe.Beside each birds' name is its Shetland equivalent. 1.herring gull {maa 2.common tern {tirrick 3.fulmar {maallie 4.oyster catcher {shalder 5.raven {corbi 6.hooded crow {craa 7.eider duck {dunter 8.wheatear {staneshakker 9.ringed plover {sandiloo 10.snipe {horse gok 11.turnstone {stenpekker 12.dunlin {ebbsleeper 13.mallard {stock duk 14.whimbrel {tang whaap 15.rock pipit {teetik 16.twite {linti 17.red throated diver {rain gos 18.shag {scarf
